paragraph.value: Let us now compare the performance of CIPHER-AVG with that of a vanilla supervised neural model.11 Table 3 shows precision, recall, and F1 scores for the NOUN tag.  Even though CIPHER-AVG achieved mixed results (mid to low accuracy), the model robustly achieves mid-range performance according to F1-score for all CLs.  The results are even more optimistic in terms of recall for English and French, and in terms of precision for Farsi and Swahili.
